《'''普罗米修斯'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Prometheus'''''}}）<!--is an original motion picture soundtrack to the -->是2012年[[普罗米修斯_(电影)|同名]][[科幻电影|科幻电影]]的电影原声碟。由德国音乐家{{link-en|马克·斯特雷腾菲尔德|Marc Streitenfeld}}主创的原声碟中也包含有两首由英国作曲家[[哈利·葛瑞森-威廉斯|哈利·葛瑞森-威廉斯]]创作的额外曲目<!--Written by German composer [[Marc_Streitenfeld|Marc Streitenfeld]], the soundtrack also features two supplemental pieces by English composer [[Harry_Gregson-Williams|Harry Gregson-Williams]],--><ref name="Soundtrack4">{{cite web|first=|last=|title=Prometheus (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack)|url=http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/prometheus-original-motion/id527304464|publisher=[[iTunes|iTunes]]|work=|date=2012-05-15|accessdate=2012-05-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723222645/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/prometheus-original-motion/id527304464|archivedate=2013-07-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>，由{{link-en|本·福斯特 (演奏家)|Ben Foster (orchestrator)|本·福斯特}}指挥演奏<!-- and it was conducted by [[Ben_Foster_(orchestrator)|Ben Foster]].--><ref name="Allthemusiccredits">{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/prometheus-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-mw0002354343/credits|title=''Prometheus'' [Original Motion Picture Soundtrack] - credits|accessdate=2012-06-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525130444/https://www.allmusic.com/album/prometheus-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-mw0002354343/credits|archivedate=2018-05-25}}</ref><ref name="Soundtrack2">{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.co.uk/Prometheus-Original-Motion-Picture-Soundtrack/dp/tracks/B007TBCTRK/ref=dp_tracks_all_1#disc_1 |title=Prometheus [Soundtrack] |publisher=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]]|date=2012-05-10|accessdate=2012-05-27 | archiveurl= |archivedate= |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

==制作==
{{see also|普罗米修斯 (电影)}}
<!--Marc Streitenfeld is a frequent collaborator with Ridley Scott.-->马克·斯特雷腾菲尔德之前曾与[[雷德利·斯科特|雷德利·斯科特]]有过多次合作，《普罗米修斯》是两人的第五次合作<ref name="Music1">{{cite news | url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/52276 | title=Is This The First Prometheus Poster?? | publisher=Ain't It Cool|accessdate=2014-01-05 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130815140520/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/52276 |archivedate=2013-08-15|deadurl=no}}</ref>。配乐录制在英国[[伦敦|伦敦]]的[[阿比路录音室|阿比路录音室]]只花了一个多星期，在一支90人的[[管弦乐团|管弦乐团]]的演奏下完成<!-- The score was recorded over one week with a 90-piece orchestra at [[Abbey_Road_Studios|Abbey Road Studios]] in London, England,--><ref name="SME">{{cite web|url=http://staticmass.net/exclusive-interviews/marc-streitenfeld-prometheus-composer/|title=Marc Streitenfeld|author=Patrick Samuel|publisher=Static Mass Emporium|date=2012-05-31|accessdate=2012-06-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68UdO9yAJ?url=http://staticmass.net/exclusive-interviews/marc-streitenfeld-prometheus-composer/|archivedate=2012-06-17}}</ref>，该录音室也同样被用于斯科特的影片后期处理<!--where it was also processed by Scott after the fact.--><ref name="MiscWonderCon12">{{cite web |first=Christina |last=Radish |title=Director Ridley Scott, Writer Damon Lindelof and Michael Fassbender Talk Prometheus at WonderCon 2012 |url=http://collider.com/ridley-scott-damon-lindelof-michael-fassbender-prometheus-interview/153243/ |publisher=Collider.com |work= |date=2012-03-18 |accessdate=2012-03-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68TNq5dm1?url=http://collider.com/ridley-scott-damon-lindelof-michael-fassbender-prometheus-interview/153243/ |archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在影片开机之前读过剧本之后，斯特雷腾菲尔德就开始对配乐进行构思。为了创作出“令人不安”的音乐效果，他规定乐队将乐谱拆散后分段倒过来演奏，之后再通过数码转制倒回来<!--Streitenfeld began coming up with ideas for the score after reading the script prior to the commencement of filming. To create an "unsettling" sound, he provided the orchestra with reversed music sheets to have them play segments of the score backwards, before then digitally reversing it.--><ref name="SME"/>。乐曲《Friend from the Past》的曲调来源于[[杰瑞·戈德史密斯|杰瑞·戈德史密斯]]在《[[异形|异形]]》{{link-en|异形 (原声碟)|Alien (soundtrack)|原声碟}}中原作的主旋律<!-- The track "Friend from the Past" reprises [[Jerry_Goldsmith|Jerry Goldsmith]]'s original main title from the [[Alien_(soundtrack)|''Alien'' soundtrack]].[[弗雷德里克·肖邦|弗雷德里克·肖邦]]的{{link-en|雨滴前奏曲|Raindrop prelude}}（1838）也被运用在电影中<ref name="MusicChopin1">{{cite journal|last=Wood|first=Michael|title=At the Movies|journal=London Review of Books|volume=34|issue=13|pages=39|url=http://www.lrb.co.uk/v34/n13/michael-wood/at-the-movies|date=2012-07-05|accessdate=2014-1-5|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6AWe8ZDQw?url=http://www.lrb.co.uk/v34/n13/michael-wood/at-the-movies|archivedate=2012-09-08|deadurl=no|author=}}</ref>--><ref name="MusicChopin2">{{cite web|last=Murphy|first=James|title=Prometheus Proves Classical Music Still Matters|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/james-murphy/prometheus-classical-music_b_1605665.html|work=Huffington Post|date=2012-06-19|accessdate=2012-09-08|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6AWeCZiqM?url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/james-murphy/prometheus-classical-music_b_1605665.html|archivedate=2012-09-08|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

==发行==
《普罗米修斯》原声专辑2012年5月15日在[[iTunes|iTunes商店]]上架销售<ref name="Soundtrack3">{{cite web |first=Glen |last=Oliver |title=Ample Sample Clips From Prometheus' Score Are Now Online!! |url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/55757 |publisher=Ain't It Cool News |work= |date=2012-05-15 |accessdate=2012-05-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68UdTV9zZ?url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/55757 |archivedate=2012-06-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，同年6月4日在英国发售音乐CD<ref name="Soundtrack1">{{cite web|url=http://www.weylandchronicles.com/2012/04/prometheus-soundtrack-now-available-for-pre-order/|title=Prometheus Soundtrack now available for pre-order|publisher=The Weyland Chronicles (weylandchronicles.com)|date=2012-04-14|accessdate=2012-06-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113124730/http://www.weylandchronicles.com/2012/04/prometheus-soundtrack-now-available-for-pre-order/|archivedate=2014-01-13|deadurl=no}}</ref>。而在美国，音乐CD则在2012年6月12日发售。

